          <formatted-text>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>Food availability varies significantly across countries, indicating uneven access to nutrition and resources </run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
        <zone flipboard-zone-id='5' h='25104' hidden='true' id='10' story-point-id='2' type-v2='text' w='18406' x='80217' y='46992'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>Dietary patterns vary across countries, with some relying heavily on carbohydrates while others have more diversified nutrient intake. </run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
        <zone flipboard-zone-id='5' h='21058' hidden='true' id='11' story-point-id='3' type-v2='text' w='18209' x='79528' y='47614'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>Countries face a dual challenge where undernourishment and obesity coexist due to shifting dietary patterns. </run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
        <zone flipboard-zone-id='5' h='21577' hidden='true' id='12' story-point-id='4' type-v2='text' w='15256' x='81299' y='46473'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>Food systems influence availability and access, but efficiency in converting supply into nutrition varies significantly. </run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
        <zone flipboard-zone-id='5' h='24481' hidden='true' id='13' story-point-id='5' type-v2='text' w='17913' x='80315' y='38900'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>Modern food systems simultaneously produce hunger and obesity, highlighting structural inefficiencies in global nutrition. </run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
      </zones>
      <simple-id uuid='{2BFD27E2-89F6-4669-A3CE-AC9291E5BDCD}' />
    </dashboard>
